image_analysis.description: A photograph taken through a doorway into a small storage or utility room. The room is cluttered with various items including tools, boxes, and cleaning supplies. There is a black countertop with a sink drain visible underneath. Above the counter are white cabinets, and one ceiling tile is missing, revealing wires and structural components. A yellow power drill is prominent on the counter. On the floor, there are several bags, a tool kit, and a spool of wire.
image_analysis.layout: Interior room shot framed by a doorway.
